'''Nyiranyamibwa Suzana''', umuririmbyi w'umunyarwandakazi w’inararibonye waboneye benshi izuba mu bahanzi nyarwanda yagarutse gutura mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] by’iteka nyuma y’[[imyaka]] irenga 40 yari amaze mu imahanga ya kure.

== UBUZIMA BWITE ==
'''Nyiranyamibwa Suzana [yavutse 1943]''' yavuye mu [[Rwanda]] mu 1973 ahunze itoteza n’[[Umwicanyi wa ruhongohongo|ubwicanyi]] bwa hato na hato bwakorerwaga [[abatutsi]]. Yabanje kuba muri [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Repubulika]] [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Iharanira]] [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Demokarasi]] [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|ya Congo]] ahava nyuma y[[Imyaka|’imyaka]] 16 yerekeza mu [[Ububiligi|Bubiligi]].

Uyu [[Umuhanzi Kamariza|muhanz]]<nowiki/>i n’[[Umuryango w’Abibumye|umuryango]] we bahunze nyuma y’uko se yishwe aroshywe mu [[Isumo rya Rusumo|Rusumo]] mu mwaka wa 1963. Nyina, '''Mukanzigiye Carolina''' na we yazize [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|Jenoside]] [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|yakorewe]] [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|Abatutsi]] [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|mu 1994]] ubwo yari avuye mu [[Ububiligi|Bubiligi]] kwivuza no gusura [[Umuryango w’Abibumye|umuryango]] we wari warahungiyeyo. yagize Ati “Data bamwishe muri 1963, ari muri baba bandi baroshywe mu [[Isumo rya Rusumo|Rusumo]] hariya i Kibungo ubu ni mu [[akarere ka Ngoma]] [[Intara y’Iburasirazuba|intara y'uburasirazuba]], mu 1973<ref>https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5527081.html?fbclid=IwAR2daxTVeLaaWmyqO9o_O51vy-B0utdu3Gdo_80Fudj8hsPWFIa3fm6-5dU</ref> nibwo twavuye mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] twari [[abana]] icyenda buri wese yagiye ukwe dushaka [[ubuzima]] turakura bigenda uko.” Yongeraho ati “Muri [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Congo]] nahageze mu 1973<ref>https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/5527081.html?fbclid=IwAR2daxTVeLaaWmyqO9o_O51vy-B0utdu3Gdo_80Fudj8hsPWFIa3fm6-5dU</ref>, nahunganye n’umugabo wanjye, mu [[Urugo rwa Yezu Nyirimpuhwe mu Ruhango|urugo]] twari [[abana]] icyenda ariko buri wese yagiye ukwe tujya gushaka ubundi [[Ubuzima|buzima]]Nahunganye n’umugabo twabyaranye [[Umwana|abana]] bane we yaguye muri [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Congo]] icyo gihe. Nahabaye [[imyaka]] 16 mpava njya kuba i [https://www.bruxelles.be/ Bruxelles]<ref>https://www.bruxelles.be/</ref> ari naho nari ntuye iyo [[imyaka]] yose.”<ref>https://www.afrocharts.com/artist?id=27d6656a2f</ref><ref>https://www.igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/umuhanzi-nyiranyamibwa-yaje-gutura-i-kigali-nyuma-y-imyaka-40-aba-mu-mahanga?fbclid=IwAR2f-KVFgmLRJZ3oshzGkpQXaW6OJyarqUbLfGC7HqOOOvvH4Da-lO8dd4M</ref>

== MU RWANDA ==
'''Nyiranyamibwa Suzana''' w’imyaka 79 avuga ko mu [[Imyaka|myaka]] yamaze [[Iburayi|i Burayi]] atigeze ahakunda kurusha u [[Rwanda]] ari nacyo cyamushyizemo imbaraga arataha ngo asazire mu [[Igihugu|gihugu]] cye cyu [[Rwanda]]. Ni [[Rimwe|umwe]] mu abaririmbyi b’[[Imana|imena]] bashinze [https://www.igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/itorero-isamaza-ryaba-rigiye-kubyutsa-umutwe-nyuma-y-imyaka-20-risenyutse itorero Isamaza]<ref>https://www.igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/itorero-isamaza-ryaba-rigiye-kubyutsa-umutwe-nyuma-y-imyaka-20-risenyutse</ref><ref>https://umuseke.rw/2021/07/kaligirwa-wanditse-turaje-indege-irahinda-na-girubuntu-zaririmbwe-nitorero-isamaza-ni-muntu-ki/amp/</ref><ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/73791/nyiranyamibwa-ushaka-kugarura-itorero-isamaza-asanga-hagahin-73791.html</ref> ryagize uruhare rukomeye mu gutiza umurindi [https://rpfinkotanyi.rw/index.php?id=371 ingabo]<ref>https://rpfinkotanyi.rw/index.php?id=371</ref> ku rugamba rwo kubohora u [[Rwanda]]. Icyo gihe yaririmbanaga n’abahanzi bari bakunzwe icyo [[Igiherero|igihe]] barimo bakomeye mu ijyana ya kinyarwanda  n’abandi babyinaga cyane.Ntabwo nigeze nkunda u [[Burayi]], nahabeshejwe n’uko nari mfite [[abana]] bagombaga kwiga kandi nkaba hafi yabo nkabitaho. Ntabwo nari gushobora kuguma hariya, mu [[Burayi]] ntabwo ari ahantu ho gusazira.” Yavuze ko nyuma yo kuza gutura mu [[Rwanda]] agiye gukomeza guhanga [[Indirimbo y’igihugu|indirimbo]] nshya ndetse ngo nibimushobokera azongera ahuze [[Umugore|abakecuru]] yaririmbanye na bo mu Isamaza bongere bahange.<ref>https://www.igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/umuhanzi-nyiranyamibwa-yaje-gutura-i-kigali-nyuma-y-imyaka-40-aba-mu-mahanga?fbclid=IwAR2f-KVFgmLRJZ3oshzGkpQXaW6OJyarqUbLfGC7HqOOOvvH4Da-lO8dd4M</ref>

=== ITORERO ISAMAZA ===



'''Nyiranyamibwa Suzana''' ari mubashinze [[Umuziki gakondo w'u Rwanda|Itorero Isamaza]] ryashingiwe mu [[Ububiligi|Bubiligi]] mu [[Imyaka|myaka]] igera kuri 30 ishize, ryatangiye rigizwe n’abiganjemo [[Umugore|abagore]] n’inkumi zabyinaga hagamijwe gushakisha ubufasha bwo gushyigikira [https://rpfinkotanyi.rw/index.php?id=371 ingabo]<ref>https://rpfinkotanyi.rw/index.php?id=371</ref> zarwanye urugamba rwo kwihobora mu 1990<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1990</ref>. [[Umuziki gakondo w'u Rwanda|Isamaze]] rigitangira ryabarizwagamo abahanzi b’abahanga barimo nka '''Nyiranyamibwa Suzana''', '''Jeanne Karigirwa Ruboneka'''<ref>https://umuseke.rw/2021/07/kaligirwa-wanditse-turaje-indege-irahinda-na-girubuntu-zaririmbwe-nitorero-isamaza-ni-muntu-ki/amp/</ref>, '''Anonciata Gatera,''' '''Francoise Ruboneka''', '''Anonciata Kayisire''' n’abandi batandukanye.<ref>https://www.igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/umuhanzi-nyiranyamibwa-yaje-gutura-i-kigali-nyuma-y-imyaka-40-aba-mu-mahanga?fbclid=IwAR2f-KVFgmLRJZ3oshzGkpQXaW6OJyarqUbLfGC7HqOOOvvH4Da-lO8dd4M</ref>

'''Nyiranyamibwa Suzana''' [[Rimwe|umwe]] mu bashinze [[Umuziki gakondo w'u Rwanda|Itorero Isamaza]] yavuze ko nyuma yo kugaruka gutura mu [[Rwanda]] ateganya kongera guhuza [[Umugore|abakecuru]] bagenzi be bakiriho bakongera kuririmba nk’itsinda no gukora ibitaramo by’[[Indirimbo y’igihugu|indirimbo]] ahanini zibutsa abantu [[Igiherero|ibihe]] iri torero ryagize mu [[Imyaka|myaka]] yashize. Ati “Abo twahoranye mu '''[[Umuziki gakondo w'u Rwanda|itorero Isamaza]]''' benshi baracyariho ariko babivuyemo, uwari umuhanga cyane mu bo twaririmbanye yaratabarutse ni '''Jeanne Karigirwa''' abandi barashatse iby’[[UMUZIKI|imiziki]] babivamo Ubwo nanjye ngiye kugerageza ndebe ko twakongera gukora ariko biragoye.”<ref>https://www.igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/itorero-isamaza-ryaba-rigiye-kubyutsa-umutwe-nyuma-y-imyaka-20-risenyutse</ref>

'''Nyiranyamibwa''' avuga ko hari [[Indirimbo y’igihugu|indirimbo]] yahimbye ariko zitarasohoka gusa arateganya kuzazishyira hanze kuri [[:en:Album|album]]<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Album</ref> nshya azamurika mu [[Igiherero|gihe]] kiri imbere. Mu kwihuza n’abahoze bagize [[Umuziki gakondo w'u Rwanda|Isamaza]] ngo yifuza ko bakora ibitaramo bito no guhanga [[Indirimbo y’igihugu|indirimbo]] nshya gusa ngo ni [[Akazi Kanoze (AKA)|akazi]] gasaba imbaraga nyinshi. Ati “Abakobwa twaririmbanye hafi ya bose iby’[[UMUZIKI|umuziki]] ntibakibyiyumvamo, bari bafite amajwi meza, ni abahanga gusa ngira ngo murabazi, bamaze gushaka baba bahagaritse [[UMUZIKI|umuziki]] abandi barabiretse  Nzagerageza gushaka uko nakongera kubabwira duhure twongere dukore ariko birasaba imbaraga.” Iyo umubajije [[Urwibutso rwa Jenoside rwa Kigali|urwibutso]] afite ku [[Umuziki gakondo w'u Rwanda|Itorero Isamaza]] asubiza yitsitsa cyane ku bumwe no kutiganda byarangaga abaririmbyi ndetse no guharanira iterambere rya buri wese byabarangaga.<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/73791/nyiranyamibwa-ushaka-kugarura-itorero-isamaza-asanga-hagahin-73791.html</ref><ref>https://www.igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/umuhanzi-nyiranyamibwa-yaje-gutura-i-kigali-nyuma-y-imyaka-40-aba-mu-mahanga?fbclid=IwAR2f-KVFgmLRJZ3oshzGkpQXaW6OJyarqUbLfGC7HqOOOvvH4Da-lO8dd4M</ref>

